title: KitchenAid® Sausage Stuffer Attachment
description:
For additional information on the featured product please visit: http://www.surlatable.com/product/PRO-691329/KitchenAid+Sausage+Stuffer+Attachment

Ideal for making homemade bratwurst, kielbasa, and Italian or Polish sausage. Includes two stuffing tubes, 3/8" and 5/8". Can be used with any KitchenAid stand mixer.
